race.comment: EXTOL (4) resumes here but the form he showed when last in work was good enough for a race of this nature. Shed his maiden tag first up last campaign at this course. Drawn well and can return a winner. FUTURE SOLDIER (5) broke the maiden status here at the latest effort and will have taken a stack of confidence from that victory. Gets 2kg off with the claim and no reason why he cannot salute again. TICKLE MY TOSEN (7) resumes. Showed glimpses of real promise last campaign, in particular when winning his maiden by 4.5 lengths at this course and distance. SAVVY BEE (9) rounds out the main chances.
